<topic template="Default" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">How to use an STB Proxy</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">How to use an STB Proxy</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">How to use an STB Proxy</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">You indicate that you wish to change the way an objects is filed by adding an </text><text styleclass="Class Name" translate="true">#stbSaveOn</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">:</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> instance method to your class. This controls the </text><text styleclass="Class Name" translate="true">STBOutFiler</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> passed as a parameter while filing the instance. Your #</text><text styleclass="Class Name" translate="true">stbSaveOn</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">: method must perform one of the following operations:</text></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">To let the filer output the receiver in the normal way (this is the default inherited from Object):</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Code Example" style="margin-left:24px;"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">STBOutFiler&gt;&gt;#saveObject: self.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">or</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example" style="margin-left:24px;"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">STBOutFiler&gt;&gt;#saveObject: self as: 0.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example" style="margin-left:24px;"></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">To output nil instead of the receiver:</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Code Example" style="margin-left:24px;"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">STBOutFiler&gt;&gt;#saveObject: self as: nil.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">To output a proxy in place of the receiver:</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Code Example" style="margin-left:24px;"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">STBOutFiler&gt;&gt;#saveObject: self as: anSTBProxy.</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
